citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:45 am on 1
September 2022.
Inspector honked vehicle horn, called and texted phone number; knocked on house entry door; family member informed
that the licensee was gone for the day.
End Section
